le%20life%2C%20they%20found%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20high%20and%20dreamed%20of%20slowing%20down.%20They%20were%20also%20worried%20about%20school%20safety%20and%20their%20kids%20growing%20up%20in%20what%20they%20saw%20as%20a%20highly%20competitive%2C%20consumption-driven%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20opportunity%20to%20sell%20their%20veterinary%20practice%20arose%2C%20the%20couple%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhen-can-i-retire%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echance%20to%20retire%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20make%20a%20lifestyle%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20relocated%20abroad%20for%20career%20opportunities%2C%20retirement%2C%20or%20lower%20living%20costs%3F%20We%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Fill%20out%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdxVL1zX0AV0FiTKnYB72xTcK5G4gxa8o5PwKsxTEwmgZJg1A%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshort%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20story%20with%20a%20reporter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20soul-searching%20about%20what%20we%20really%20wanted%20our%20lives%20to%20look%20like%20and%20what%20we%20wanted%20our%20kids'%20lives%20to%20look%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%2C%2065%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20knew%20they%20wanted%20to%20leave%20the%20cold%20behind%2C%20but%20they%20couldn't%20think%20of%20anywhere%20else%20in%20the%20US%20they%20wanted%20to%20live.%20Instead%2C%20they%20kept%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcosta-rica-trip-what-to-pack-list-mistakes-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECosta%20Rica%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20country%20they'd%20visited%20multiple%20times%20and%20loved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222697%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Las%20Catalinas%20in%20Costa%20Rica.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22ht