residence%20is%20the%20second%20property%20they've%20owned%20in%20Costa%20Rica.%20They%20said%20they%20sold%20their%20first%20house%20in%20Las%20Catalinas%20for%20around%20%241.5%20million%20before%20purchasing%20a%20larger%20home%20nearby%20for%20%241.6%20million%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20spent%20roughly%20%24200%2C000%20upgrading%20it.%20The%20home%20sits%20steps%20from%20the%20beach%20and%20features%20a%20pool%20and%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20annual%20property%20taxes%20in%20the%20US%20were%20about%20%2415%2C000.%20Now%2C%20they%20pay%20around%20%245%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20comparable%20beachfront%20house%20would%20likely%20have%20been%20out%20of%20reach%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Andrew%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20that%20anywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20the%20couple%20appreciates%20most%20about%20the%20town%20is%20its%20strong%20sense%20of%20community.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20they%20rarely%20interacted%20with%20their%20neighbors.%20Here%2C%20it's%20common%20to%20run%20into%20people%20they%20know%20while%20walking%20through%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20sons%20attend%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-studied-china-universities-cheaper-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20formed%20friendships%20with%20kids%20of%20different%20ages%20and%20backgrounds%2C%20Andrew%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20walkability%20of%20the%20town%20has%20been%20so%20great%20for%20the%20kids%2C%20because%20they%20can%20just%20go%20out%20and%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20them%20getting%20hit%20by%20a%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20Allyson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20dining%20area.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a339ea84074dae0e204552f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20say%20their%20kids%20get%20to%20have%20more%20freedom%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20than%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Allyson%20Rappaport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20their%20sons%20regularly%20participated%20in%20active-shooter%20drills%20at%20school%2C%20something%20Allyson%20found%20deeply%20unsettling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20kids%20were%20going%20to%20grow%20up%20in%20this%20environment%20where%20you%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20being%20shot%20in%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20some%20place%20I'd%20want%20to%20raise%20my%20kids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22491dfea5-4674-45f2-bee7-e89ec27aeb0b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20reality%20of%20starting%20over%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rappaports%20are%20among%20many%20Americans%20who%20have%20chosen%20to%20make%20Costa%20Rica%20home.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcr.usembassy.gov%2Fpolicy-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Embassy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20approximately%20120%2C000%20Americans%20live%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20that%20Costa%20Rica%20offers%20multiple%20residency%20options%20for%20foreigners%2C%20including%20visas%20geared%20toward%20retirees%2C%20digital%20nomads%2C%20and%20investors.%20The%20investor%20program%20allows%20foreigners%20to%20qualify%20for%20residency%20by%20making%20a%20minimum%20%24150%2C000%20investment%20in%20the%20country%2C%20including%20in%20real%20estate%20%E2%80%94%20the%20route%20the%20Rappaports%20took.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20spoken%20to%20several%20Americans%20who%20have%20relocated%20to%20Costa%20Rica%20in%20recent%20years.%20Many%20pointed%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-us-to-costa-rica-afford-life-we-wanted-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecountry's%20affordability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-colorado-to-costa-rica-blue-zone-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslower%20pace%20of%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffired-moved-costa-rica-built-own-business-happy-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutdoor%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20reasons%20for%20making%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20moving%20abroad%20came%20with%20a%20learning%20curve%20for%20the%20Rappaports.%20While%20English%20is%20widely%20spoken%20in%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20the%20family%20initially%20struggled%20with%20the%20language%20barrier.%20Now%2C%20they%20are%20fluent%20in%20Spanish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a339ef3564c774507cd4290%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20miss%20some%20of%20the%20conveniences%20of%20American%20life%2C%20but%20say%20living%20abroad%20has%20made%20them%20more%20conscious%20consumers.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Allyson%20Rappaport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%20comes%20with%20trade-offs%2C%20too.%20Everyday%20tasks%20and%20bureaucratic%20processes%20often%20take%20longer%20than%20they%20would%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20the%20couple%20said%20it's%20simply%20part%20of%20adapting%20to%20a%20different%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPura%20Vida%2C%20that's%20the%20local%20thing.%20Like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20it's%20all%20good.%20Pura%20Vida!%26quot%3B%20Allyson%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20Costa%20Rican%20phrase%20that's%20often%20used%20to%20express%20a%20laid-back%2C%20optimistic%20attitude%20toward%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there%20are%20aspects%20of%20life%20in%20the%20US%20that%20the%20Rappaports%20miss.%20Specialty%20ingredients%20are%20sometimes%20hard%20to%20come%20by%2C%20and%20online%20shopping%20isn't%20nearly%20as%20convenient%20or%20accessible%20as%20it%20was%20back%20in%20Connecticut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Allyson%20sees%20an%20upside%3A%20The%20family%20has%20become%20more%20mindful%20about%20what%20they%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22490%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20outdoor%20patio.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a339f3a564c774507cd4292%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22368%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20now%20speak%20Spanish%20fluently%20and%20have%20since%20adapted%20to%20the%20slower%20pace%20of%20life.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Allyson%20Rappaport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20realize%2C%20maybe%20I%20don't%20really%20even%20need%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20the%20Rappaports%20say%20they%20get%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20more%20time%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20kids%20have%20us%20growing%20up%2C%20both%20of%20us.%20We're%20at%20all%20the%20functions%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERunning%20errands%20also%20takes%20more%20time%20than%20it%20did%20in%20the%20US.%20A%20trip%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20a%20car%20service%20appointment%2C%20or%20other%20routine%20tasks%20can%20easily%20take%20several%20hours%2C%20Andrew%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20say%20to%20me%2C%20'Aren't%20you%20bored%20all%20the%20time%3F'%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20fill%20every%20day.%20There's%20really%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20downtime%2C%20yet%20we%20never%20feel%20rushed%20or%20pushed%20or%20stressed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20chore-free%20day%2C%20that%20lack%20of%20urgency%20is%20easy%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20making%20breakfast%20and%20getting%20the%20kids%20ready%20for%20school%2C%20Allyson%20heads%20to%20the%20tennis%20courts%20before%20the%20couple%20meets%20for%20lunch.%20In%20the%20afternoons%2C%20they're%20often%20at%20the%20beach%2C%20by%20the%20pool%2C%20or%20working%20out%20at%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%20has%20benefited%20their%20marriage%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20after%20seven%20years%2C%20it%20still%20feels%20like%20we're%20living%20on%20vacation%2C%26quot%3B%20Allyson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-costa-rica-kids-taxes-car-free-town-slow-life-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782688441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a339d952bbd1d834ef254e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-costa-rica-kids-taxes-car-free-town-slow-life-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20fill%20every%20day.%20There's%20really%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20downtime%2C%20yet%20we%20never%20feel%20rushed%20or%20pushed%20or%20stressed%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Rappaport%20told%20BI%20about%20life%20in%20Costa%20Rica.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Daemon%20and%20Rhaenyra%20scene%20with%20Daenerys%20reference%20goes%20viral%20-%20WATCH%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782687810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132060391%2Cimgsize-141688.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fhouse-of-the-dragon-season-3-daemon-and-rhaenyra-scene-goes-viral-as-fans-spot-daenerys-targaryen-reference-watch%2Farticleshow%2F132060368.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132060368.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDaenerys%20Targaryen%2C%20the%20iconic%20Mother%20of%20Dragons%20from%20'Game%20of%20Thrones'%2C%20is%2