0meaningful%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20learning%20that%20family%20connection%20changes%20shape%20as%20children%20get%20older%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20the%20last%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-husband-reads-me-a-bedtime-story-most-nights-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebedtime%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20read%20my%20kids%20would%20be%20the%20last%20%3Cem%3Eever%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Or%20that%20the%20last%20time%20I%20held%20them%20%E2%80%94%20or%20kissed%20a%20scraped%20knee%20or%20sang%20them%20a%20silly%20song%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20the%20last%20time%20I'd%20do%20any%20of%20those%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20good%20thing%2C%20of%20course.%20It%20saved%20me%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20from%20the%20pain%20of%20knowing%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-live-home-intergenerational-living-not-empty-nesters-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweet%20little%20rituals%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20coming%20to%20an%20end.%20But%20realizing%20it%20later%20opens%20the%20door%20to%20a%20new%20awareness%20of%20just%20how%20quickly%20it%20all%20goes.%20And%2C%20for%20me%20anyway%2C%20a%20new%20dread%20that%20it%20will%20be%20over%20far%20faster%20than%20I'm%20comfortable%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ab17555-5b61-4faf-9183-475b2b82bd1f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EParenting%20teens%20has%20a%20weird%20finality%20to%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20when%20your%20kids%20are%20little%2C%20and%20their%20needy%20period%20seems%20to%20drag%20infinitely%20(and%20exhaustingly)%20on%2C%20there's%20this%20weird%20sense%20of%20finality%20when%20you're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-one-taught-me-how-to-parent-a-teenager-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparenting%20teens%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20young%20adults.%20Because%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20happens%20as%20your%20kids%20get%20older%20is%20that%20you%20realize%20just%20how%20painfully%20true%20that%20adage%20is%20%E2%80%94%20you%20know%2C%20the%20one%20you%20rolled%20your%20eyes%20at%20as%20the%20weary%20parent%20of%20a%20toddler%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BThe%20days%20are%20long%2C%20but%20the%20years%20are%20short.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221099%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20with%20son%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3026ada4629406118995b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22824%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20time%20does%20fly%20when%20raising%20kids.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20another%20thing%20that%20happens%20when%20they%20get%20older%20is%20that%20they%20pull%20away.%20One%20minute%2C%20you%20can't%20even%20make%20a%20solo%20trip%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%20and%20the%20next%2C%20between%20friends%20and%20extracurriculars%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearn-extra-money-with-these-21-high-paying-side-jobs-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epart-time%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you're%20practically%20begging%20them%20to%20hang%20out%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20like%20any%20mom%20who's%20secretly%20feeling%20desperate%20to%20grasp%20any%20moment%20of%20connection%20she%20can%2C%20I%20made%20my%20four%20boys%2C%20ranging%20in%20age%20from%2013%20to%2020%2C%20an%20offer%20they%20couldn't%20refuse%3A%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-do-family-vacations-get-better-easier-enjoyable-kids-age-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20vacation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20them%2C%20it%20was%20a%20trip%20to%20Beaches%20Turks%20and%20Caicos.%20To%20their%20dad%20and%20me%2C%20it%20was%20a%20precious%20chance%20to%20soak%20up%20these%20last%20few%20opportunities%20for%20complete%20togetherness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22682d037b-f6d4-480e-a1aa-f17da02a8eef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20can%20see%20the%20empty%20nest%20coming%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20all%20still%20living%20at%20home%2C%20but%20our%20oldest%20will%20soon%20turn%2021%2C%20our%20second%20is%20graduating%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20our%20third%20graduates%20next%20year%2C%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bbaby%26quot%3B%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-high-school-adults-miss-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentering%20high%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20so%20we're%20all%20too%20aware%20that%20we're%20hurtling%20toward%20an%20empty%20nest%20at%20breakneck%20speed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20we%20won't%20be%20there%20for%20a%20few%20years%20yet%2C%20our%20time%20as%20a%20family%20of%20six%20is%20dwindling%20fast%3B%20this%20vacation%20was%20the%20perfect%20way%20to%20create%20those%20last%20few%20memories%20while%20we're%20still%20all%20together.%20And%20what%20better%20place%20to%20do%20it%20than%20in%20a%20literal%20paradise%2C%20where%20even%20the%20moodiest%20teenager%20can't%20help%20but%20be%20a%20little%20less%20surly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221011%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20and%20son%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3025f90b873a3c9460cd6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22758%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20reflects%20on%20how%20quickly%20her%20kids%20turned%20into%20teens.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20I'd%20have%20been%20in%20my%20PJs%20by%207%20p.m.%2C%20but%20bolstered%20by%20the%20warm%20Caribbean%20breeze%2C%20we%20ventured%20out%20for%20the%20Friday%20night%20street%20party%2C%20led%20by%20a%20vibrant%20parade%20of%20dancers%20and%20musicians%20with%20an%20intoxicating%20beat.%20I%20can't%20recall%20the%20last%20time%20my%20kids%20and%20I%20smiled%20and%20danced%20to%20the%20same%20music%2C%20but%20miraculously%2C%20here%20we%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9964fb2-602a-4f6e-bf93-faaa2cf16a2d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatching%20my%20boys%20become%20men%20happened%20gradually%20%E2%80%94%20and%20all%20at%20once%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20help%20watch%20the%20parents%20with%20their%20toddlers%20in%20tow%2C%20wishing%20I%20could%20magically%20compel%20them%20to%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20savor%20this%20time%20with%20their%20littles%2C%20like%20some%20harbinger%20from%20the%20future.%20But%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20things%20you%20only%20%3Cem%3Etruly%3C%2Fem%3E%20realize%20once%20those%20days%20are%20behind%20you%2C%20so%20I%20just%20looked%20at%20my%20own%20kids%20and%20reflected.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20rounded%20faces%20have%20sharpened%20into%20jawlines%2C%20their%20voices%20have%20deepened%20into%20those%20of%20men%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20pick%20any%20of%20them%20up%20if%20I%20tried.%20It%20happened%20so%20fast.%20And%20it%20makes%20me%20realize%20the%20importance%20of%20taking%20these%20moments%20when%20I%20can%2C%20even%20if%20they%20look%20a%20little%20different%20than%20they%20used%20to.%20Because%20at%20this%20age%2C%20%26quot%3Btogether%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20always%20doing%20everything%20as%20an%20entire%20family%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c5297a2-3a51-49dd-b34d-3f7a667ca53a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20know%20if%20this%20was%20our%20last%20family%20vacation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHopefully%2C%20that's%20a%20metaphor%20for%20how%20life%20will%20go.%20They'll%20venture%20out%2C%20they'll%20experience%20things%20on%20their%20own%2C%20but%20they'll%20always%20come%20back%20to%20loop%20us%20in%20on%20how%20things%20are%20going.%20And%20maybe%2C%20hopefully%2C%20they'll%20experience%20some%20of%20those%20things%20together%2C%20even%20if%20it%20doesn't%20involve%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomeday%20we'll%20take%20our%20last-ever%20vacation%20as%20a%20family%20before%20everyone%20heads%20in%20different%20directions%3B%20whether%20it%20was%20this%20one%2C%20I%20don't%20know.%20But%20I%20do%20know%20that%20I'm%20eternally%20grateful%20we%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20squeeze%20it%20in%20before%20the%20window%20closes.%20And%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20our%20kids%20know%20that%20no%20matter%20where%20life%20takes%20them%2C%20we're%20always%20here%20when%20they%20want%20to%20come%20back%2C%20eager%20to%20hear%20every%20last%20detail%20of%20their%20adventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-vacation-before-empty-nest-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782677881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a301b6b9ab49a561171fc48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-vacation-before-empty-nest-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20family%20trip%20with%20my%20four%20teenage%20and%20young%20adult%20sons%20reminded%20me%20how%20little%20time%20we%20have%20left%20before%20the%20nest%20empties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rita%20Templeton)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Death%20of%20Robin%20Hood%E2%80%99%20Artisans%20Break%20Down%20Hugh%20Jackman%E2%80%99s%20Brutal%20Transformation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782677785000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236791235%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20artisans%20behind%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Death%20of%20Robin%20Hood%2C%E2%80%9D%20including%20hair%20designer%20Sean%20Flanigan%20and%20costume%20designer%20Lorna%20Mugan%2C%20wanted%20Hugh%20Jackman%20to%20become%20unrecognizable%20as%20Robin%20Hood.%20But%20of%20course%2C%20director%20Michael%20Sarnoski%E2%80%98s%20(%E2%80%9CPig%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CA%20Quiet%20Place%3A%20Day%20One%E2%80%9D)%20vision%20for%20Robin%20Hood%20i