-beaches-food-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EComporta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20dreamy%20village%20with%20white-sand%20beaches%2C%20pine%20forests%2C%20and%20clear%20blue%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20time%20there%2C%20I%20soaked%20in%20the%20sun%20at%20Praia%20da%20Comporta%20and%20Praia%20do%20Pego%2C%20where%20the%20ocean%20was%20the%20main%20attraction%20and%20superb%20beach%20clubs%20were%20never%20too%20far%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20Comporta%20Caf%C3%A9%20Beach%20Club%2C%20which%20was%20nestled%20in%20the%20dunes%20of%20Praia%20da%20Comporta%20and%20offered%20plenty%20of%20delicious%2C%20traditional%20Portuguese%20seafood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20highlights%20of%20my%20visit%20was%20horseback%20riding%20right%20on%20the%20beach.%20I%20visited%20a%20local%20equestrian%20school%20that%20offered%20scenic%20trail%20rides%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20while%20riding%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20Madonna%20was%20a%20frequent%20visitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20true%20gem%20that%20offers%20serenity%2C%20great%20food%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20adventure%2C%20I'd%20plan%20a%20trip%20to%20Comporta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea182ea4-6e82-4f36-af59-2c79f26f6452%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGozo%2C%20an%20island%20located%20in%20the%20Maltese%20archipelago%2C%20is%20relaxing%20and%20unique%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Coastal%20bay%20with%20turquoise%20water%20and%20cliffs%20viewed%20from%20inside%20a%20rocky%20cave%20opening%20in%20Gozo.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d616fa25092c74cc9f4c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMixta%20Cave%20was%20a%20highlight%20of%20my%20Gozo%20trip.%3Cp%3ESara%20Sturek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMalta%20had%20been%20on%20my%20list%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20its%20sister%20island%2C%20Gozo%2C%20would%20leave%20such%20a%20lasting%20impression.%20I%20first%20learned%20about%20this%20island%20from%20the%20owners%20of%20a%20local%20Maltese%20restaurant%2C%20who%20recommended%20that%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20there%20was%20straightforward%3A%20We%20took%20a%20quick%20ferry%20ride%20from%20Malta%2C%20and%20within%2040%20minutes%2C%20we%20were%20instantly%20awestruck%20by%20the%20island's%20dramatic%20coastline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20arrived%2C%20we%20chatted%20with%20some%20locals%20and%20learned%20about%20the%20famous%20Maxokk%20Bakery.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20the%20ftira%20%E2%80%94%20a%20flattened%20Maltese%20bread%20often%20used%20for%20sandwiches%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20well%20worth%20the%20hourslong%20wait%20times.%20After%20trying%20a%20tuna%20ftira%20and%20anchovy%20pizza%20ourselves%2C%20we%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20we%20took%20a%20quick%20ride-share%20to%20Ramla%20Bay%2C%20a%20gorgeous%20red-sand%20beach.%20After%20some%20relaxing%2C%20we%20hiked%20up%20to%20Mixta%20Cave%2C%20a%20natural%20cave%20overlooking%20Ramla%20Bay.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20highlight%20of%20our%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I%20want%20to%20stay%20for%20even%20longer%2C%20and%20explore%20towns%20and%20villages%20like%20Xlendi%20and%20Marsalforn%20%E2%80%94%20not%20only%20for%20some%20seaside%20dining%2C%20but%20to%20check%20out%20the%20diving%20scene%20and%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeautiful-natural-wonders-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enatural%20wonders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8406a00-2e54-45d6-817d-c4d2eca4c9a2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20exploring%20Croatia%2C%20Hvar%20was%20my%20favorite%20spot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Small%20boats%20float%20in%20turquoise%20coastal%20water%20between%20tree-covered%20islands%20under%20a%20bright%20blue%20sky%20with%20scattered%20clouds.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22http