%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyouth-sports-expensive-competitive-huge-commitment-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplay%20travel%20baseball%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20have%20spent%20about%204%2C000%20hours%20on%20the%20bleachers%20watching%20nothing%20happen%20for%20long%20stretches.%20I%20have%20also%2C%20during%20those%20hours%2C%20written%20code%20for%20my%20AI%20startup%2C%20rehearsed%20answers%20for%20an%20investor%20interview%2C%20pressure-tested%20a%20crisis%20comms%20plan%2C%20and%20argued%20with%20Claude%20about%20the%20infield%20fly%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20see%20me%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221824%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kid%20batting%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29a80db19390180e4cfa30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221368%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20uses%20AI%20while%20watching%20her%20kids%20play%20baseball.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20easily%20be%20the%20cautionary%20tale%20about%20modeled%20behavior.%20Mom%20on%20her%20phone%2C%20missing%20the%20game%2C%20checked%20out%20behind%20a%20screen%2C%20later%20surprised%20by%20her%20kids'%20device%20addiction.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-uses-ai-manage-household-parenting-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20a%20welcome%20guest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20my%20household%2C%20and%20here's%20what%20I%20think%20my%20three%20young%20boys%20are%20learning%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228aad181e-59f2-4a54-80aa-ae56dde5d090%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20is%20not%20social%20media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20Pete%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-makes-a-great-product-leader-repost-2010-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduct%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Whip%20smart%20and%20chronically%20online%20in%20the%20way%20that%20tech%20people%20are.%20Before%20AI%2C%20he%20scrolled%20incessantly%20%E2%80%94%20X%2C%20Instagram%2C%20Slack%2C%20group%20chats%20%E2%80%94%20struggling%20to%20quiet%20his%20overactive%20mind%20with%20passive%20digital%20consumption.%20Since%20he%20started%20using%20AI%2C%20he's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-doomscrolling-tracking-film-podcasts-books-analog-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiven%20up%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20now%20spends%20his%20free%20time%20talking%20with%20Claude%2C%20interrogating%20ideas%2C%20using%20them%20to%20build%20things%2C%20and%20working%20through%20business%20problems%20that%20used%20to%20just%20rattle%20around%20in%20his%20head.%20Our%20kids%20don't%20see%20us%20doomscrolling%20anymore%3B%20they%20see%20us%20thinking%20out%20loud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d517a73-9128-4d3f-9478-8d4dc7541e9d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20tool%20reflects%20the%20person%20using%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20eldest%20son%2C%20Dash%20(13)%2C%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-max-20x-ai-plan-subscribers-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClaude%20subscription%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20started%20building%20complex%20games%20on%20Roblox.%20AI%20acts%20as%20his%20math%20tutor%20when%207th-grade%20geometry%20gets%20too%20much%20for%20his%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20Claude%20is%20really%20good%20at%20helping%20him%20with%20school%20work%2C%20but%20he%20is%20also%20aware%20that%20kids%20can%20use%20it%20to%20cheat%20on%20assignments%20and%20tests.%20He%20already%20understands%20something%20many%20adults%20don't%3A%20AI%20reflects%20the%20judgment%20of%20the%20person%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDash%20is%20also%20skeptical%20in%20ways%20adults%20often%20aren't.%20He%20complains%20that%20AI%20search%20results%20are%20frequently%20wrong%2C%20having%20once%20tried%20to%20look%20up%20the%20specs%20for%20an%20e-bike%20model%20and%20being%20confidently%20lied%20to.%20He%20rolls%20his%20eyes%20at%20what%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3Bobviously%20fake%26quot%3B%20AI-generated%20videos%20because%20the%20spelling%20in%20the%20captions%20is%20wrong%2C%20people%20appear%20to%20be%20levitating%2C%20or%20poorly%20lip-syncing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20been%20fooled%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c32faa0-4491-4c6f-9ec0-5e5b5f590b22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20only%20fear%20what%20we%20don't%20understand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20in%20tech%20PR%2C%20so%20I'm%20familiar%20with%20how%20quickly%20world-ending%20narratives%20form%20around%20new%20technology%2C%20and%20how%20rarely%20they%20capture%20what%20something%20feels%20like%20in%20practice.%20Don't%20get%20me%20wrong%2C%20I'm%20still%20fearful%20of%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20my%20kids'%20future%20jobs%2C%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20think%20critically%20or%20problem-solve%20as%20adults.%20But%20in%20our%20house%2C%20we%20engage%20intentionally%20with%20AI%20to%20better%20understand%20it%20(and%2C%20as%20a%20consequence%2C%20fear%20it%20less)%2C%20and%20replace%20lower-quality%20attention%20with%20higher-quality%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20just%20makes%20life%20run%20better%2C%20which%20is%20its%20own%20kind%20of%20demystification.%20Before%20a%20family%20trip%2C%20we%20used%20to%20spend%20hours%20down%20TripAdvisor%20rabbit%20holes%2C%20half-reading%20travel%20blogs%20written%20by%20people%20trying%20to%20sell%20us%20luggage.%20Now%20we%20listen%20to%20a%20history%20podcast%20in%20the%20rental%20car%20and%20ask%20Claude%20for%20the%20top%20five%20things%20to%20know%20about%20wherever%20we're%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDriving%20into%20Alberobello%20last%20summer%20(my%2072-year-old%20dad%20in%20the%20back%20seat%20alongside%20the%20boys)%2C%20we%20already%20knew%20we%20were%20walking%20into%20a%20UNESCO%20village%20of%201%2C500-year-old%20trulli%20%E2%80%94%20stone%20huts%20built%20without%20mortar%20so%20peasants%20could%20dismantle%20them%20fast%20when%20tax%20collectors%20came.%20Sure%2C%20we%20could%20have%20Googled%20that%2C%20but%20pulling%20up%20Claude%20and%20asking%20questions%20on%20the%20fly%20turned%20sightseeing%20into%20a%20conversation.%20Even%20my%20dad%2C%20who'd%20never%20touched%20AI%20before%20the%20trip%2C%20became%20a%20power%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20if%20any%20of%20this%20makes%20us%20an%20atypical%20family.%20As%20with%20most%20parenting%20decisions%2C%20it's%20probably%20too%20early%20to%20say%20whether%20I've%20miscalculated%20and%20will%20end%20up%20as%20the%20aforementioned%20cautionary%20tale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20know%20when%20the%20top%20of%20the%20fourth%20inning%20is%2C%20and%20that%20my%20son%20is%20stepping%20into%20the%20batter's%20box%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20I%20put%20down%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-watch-me-use-ai-every-day-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782655322000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a298bacb19390180e4cf193%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-watch-me-use-ai-every-day-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20use%20AI%20at%20baseball%20games%2C%20on%20family%20trips%2C%20and%20for%20work.%20My%20kids%20are%20learning%20how%20to%20think%20critically%20about%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rachael%20Cassidy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20writes%20a%20lot%20of%20software.%20Now%2C%20human%20code%20review%20is%20starting%20to%20disappear.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Truell%2C%20CEO%20of%20Curs