0Dells%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20go%20back.%3Cp%3EBlythe%20Chadim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalahari-water-park-wisconsin-dells-adults-review-worth-it-2024-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWisconsin%20Dells%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20many%20family-friendly%20activities%2C%20but%20its%20water%20parks%20weren't%20a%20draw%20for%20us.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOur%20big%20group%20had%20fun%20exploring%20the%20area's%20natural%20beauty%20with%20canyon%20tours%20and%20boat%20rides.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20didn't%20love%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20area's%20tourist-trap%20vibes%2C%20but%20our%20kid-friendly%20rental%20was%20great.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20my%20parents%20gifted%20my%20siblings%20and%20me%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-do-family-vacations-get-better-easier-enjoyable-kids-age-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20family%20vacation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20all%20live%20in%20different%20places%2C%20and%20getting%20together%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20there%20are%2014%20of%20us%2C%20including%20kids.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20everyone's%20schedules%2C%20it%20took%20over%20a%20year%20to%20get%20a%20trip%20on%20the%20books.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20suggested%20ideas%20for%20various%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-countries-visit-with-kids-frequent-travelers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efamily-friendly%20destinations%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20when%20my%20stepsister%20mentioned%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20heading%20to%20Wisconsin%20for%20a%20work%20trip%2C%20a%20new%20idea%20began%20to%20take%20shape%3A%20Wisconsin%20Dells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20is%20a%20popular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-region-of-united-states-to-visit-midwest-family-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMidwest%20vacation%20spot%20for%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20its%20stunning%20natural%20beauty%20and%20many%20kid-friendly%20attractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFamously%2C%20it's%20also%20considered%20the%20%26quot%3BWater%20Park%20Capital%20of%20the%20World%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20its%20high%20concentration%20of%20both%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20water%20parks%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-wolf-lodge-family-trip-cheaper-than-disney-review-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGreat%20Wolf%20Lodge%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Land%20of%20Natura.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a225677-3705-473b-b356-0e425d16ba24%5C%22%3EWe%20found%20a%20vacation%20rental%20that%20catered%20to%20families%2C%20and%20our%20kids%20didn't%20want%20to%20leave%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-us-cities-towns-to-visit-summer-frequent-traveler-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etourist%20destination%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Wisconsin%20Dells%20offers%20all%20kinds%20of%20accommodations%2C%20and%20finding%20one%20that%20fit%20our%20family%20proved%20easier%20than%20expected.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%20hotels%20and%20resorts%2C%20we%20were%20happy%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20water-park%20traffic%20in%20a%20VRBO%20vacation%20rental%20in%20a%20quiet%20neighborhood%20within%20walking%20distance%20of%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20rented%20a%20two-story%20duplex%2C%20connected%20by%20the%20garage.%20The%20main%20floors%20featured%20expansive%20living%20rooms%2C%20with%20large%20wall-mounted%20TVs%2C%20perfect%20for%20watching%20the%20NBA%20finals%20as%20a%20family.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20was%20the%20kids'%20play%20areas%20in%20each%20garage.%20I'm%20talking%20foosball%20tables%2C%20swing%20sets%2C%20play%20houses%2C%20and%20climbing%20structures%20%E2%80%94%20our%20kids%20didn't%20want%20to%20leave.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20rental%20was%20a%20highlight%20of%20our%20stay%20and%20the%20most%20kid-friendly%20place%20I've%20ever%20stayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272f18d73-9791-429c-9f47-1aa62adca2c6%5C%22%3EA%20lot%20of%20Wisconsin%20Dells%20felt%20like%20a%20tourist%20trap%2C%20which%20we%20didn't%20love%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221213%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mini%20golf%20course%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d452ae218c3b62535d07b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20prices%20of%20activities%20could%20quickly%20add%20up%20for%20a%20family.%3Cp%3EBlythe%20Chadim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalk%20down%20Broadway%2C%20and%20you'll%20find%20a%20plethora%20of%20arcades%2C%20like%20Wild%20Fun%20Zone%2C%20and%20interactive%20activities%20like%20Ripley's%20Believe%20It%20Or%20Not%2C%20Wizard%20Quest%2C%20and%20the%20aptly%20named%20Cheese%20Ball%20Croquet%20mini-golf%20course.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20destination%20is%20designed%20to%20appeal%20to%20families%2C%20but%20all%20that%20manufactured%20fun%20comes%20at%20a%20price.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20tickets%20for%20in-town%20attractions%20cost%20around%20%2420%20per%20kid%20and%20%2430%20or%20more%20per%20adult.%20Before%20you%20know%20it%2C%20you're%20dropping%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20of%20entertainment%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20additional%20expenses%20for%20snacks%20and%20other%20add-ons%20each%20place%20offers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20mostly%20chose%20not%20to%20partake%2C%20instead%20saving%20our%20money%20for%20other%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20all%20of%20that%2C%20there%20seemed%20to%20be%20souvenir%20and%20T-shirt%20shops%20on%20every%20corner.%20Walking%20through%20town%20with%20our%20kids%20felt%20like%20navigating%20a%20minefield.%20They%20were%20constantly%20asking%20to%20pop%20into%20another%20shop%2C%20buy%20an%20ice-cream%20cone%2C%20or%20play%20yet%20another%20claw%20machine.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20us%2C%20it%20was%20overwhelming%2C%20and%20by%20the%20end%2C%20we%20were%20tired%20of%20constantly%20saying%20no.%20After%20our%20initial%20walk%20through%20town%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20avoid%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ed5822f-d726-4fb1-b11e-8721298f6381%5C%22%3EOur%20kids%20loved%20the%20over-the-top%20restaurants%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221363%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paul%20Bunyan%20statue%20outside%20of%20restaurant%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d452a360acd489560b3e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaul%20Bunyan's%20Cook%20Shanty%20had%20a%20large%20statue%20of%20its%20namesake.%3Cp%3EBlythe%20Chadim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20similar%20note%2C%20every%20restaurant%20we%20visited%20had%20a%20theme%2C%20often%20paired%20with%20over-the-top%20decor%20and%20simple%20menus.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreakfast%20at%20Paul%20Bunyan's%20Cook%20Shanty%20was%20exactly%20what%20you'd%20expect%20from%20the%20name%3A%20a%20large%20wooden%20cabin%2C%20featuring%20a%20towering%20statue%20of%20Paul%20Bunyan%20and%20all-you-can-eat%20family-style%20platters%20of%20pancakes%2C%20sausages%2C%20eggs%2C%20and%20doughnuts.%20There%20was%20plenty%20of%20food%2C%20but%20the%20choices%20felt%20minimal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20dinner%2C%20we%20went%20to%20two%20well-known%20restaurants%3A%20Moosejaw%20Pizza%20%26amp%3B%20Dells%20Brewing%20Co.%20the%20first%20night%2C%20and%20Buffalo%20Phil's%20Pizza%20%26amp%3B%20Grille%20the%20next.%20The%20latter%20featured%20Lego%2C%20Star%20Wars%2C%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20decor.%20Model%20trains%20delivered%20all%20the%20food%20and%20beverages%20to%20the%20table.%20It%20was%20also%20connected%20to%20a%20massive%20arcade%2C%20something%20our%20kids%20reminded%20us%20of%20throughout%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stormtrooper%20figurine%20behind%20bar%20in%20Buff%20Phils%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d45d5a25092c74cc9f284%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20saw%20some%20cool%20decor%20at%20Buffalo%20Phil's%20Pizza%20%26amp%3B%20Grille.%3Cp%3EBlythe%20Chadim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20our%20children%20loved%20the%20fun%20decor%20and%20kid-friendly%20food%2C%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20I%20found%20the%20menus%20repetitive%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20of%20pizzas%20and%20burgers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee1d2ada-5084-4e30-8396-d03e2dfbbfb5%5C%22%3EWe%20skipped%20the%20water%20parks%20to%20enjoy%20the%20area's%20natural%20beauty%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221213%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20Dells%20River%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d452aa25092c74cc9f26b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20nice%20traveling%20around%20the%20Dells%20River.%3Cp%3EBlythe%20Chadim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20been%20much%20of%20a%20water-park%20person.%20It%20doesn't%20help%20that%20I%20burn%20super%20easily%2C%20making%20an%20entire%20day%20baking%20under%20the%20sun%20feel%20like%20a%20punishment%20rather%20than%20a%20vacation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20%3Cem%3Ewere%3C%2Fem%3E%20indoor%20options%2C%20water%20parks%20just%20didn't%20feel%20ideal%20for%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-international-trip-multiple-generations-mistakes-lessons-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emixed-age%20travel%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0which%20ranged%20from%20preschoolers%20to%20septuagenarians.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20kids%20ages%204%20and%206%20made%20that%20kind%20of%20water%20play%20even%20less%20appealing.%20They'd%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20extra-close%20supervision%20around%20all%20the%20water%2C%20and%20we%20worried%20they'd%20be%20limited%20to%20mostly%20shallow%20splash%20areas%20and%20small%20slides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20other%20fun%20activities%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20being%20home%20to%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-water-parks-us-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewater%20parks%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Noah's%20Ark%2C%20Wisconsin%20Dells%20is%20also%20known%20for%20its%20natural%20beauty%2C%20including%20towering%20sandstone%20cliffs%20and%20pine-tree%20forests.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221213%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20canyons%20in%20Wisconsin%20Dells%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d452ae218c3b62535d07d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20loved%20our%20carriage%20ride%20through%20the%20canyons.%3Cp%3EBlythe%20Chadim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20enjoyed%20some%20of%20this%20beauty%20up%20close%20on%20a%20horse-drawn%20carriage%20ride%20with%20Lost%20Canyon%20Tours%20on%20Lake%20Delton%20%E2%80%94%20perfect%20for%20the%20entire%20family.%20The%20mile-long%20ride%20through%20deep-cut%20sandstone%20gorges%20felt%20like%20a%20trip%20back%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lost%20Canyon%20yeti%20carving%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d452a360acd489560b3e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuring%20the%20carriage%20ride%2C%20we%20saw%20some%20incredible%20sights.%3Cp%3EBlythe%20Chadim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20our%20carriage%20ride%2C%20we%20took%20in%20the%20area's%20scenery%20from%20the%20water%20on%20a%20duckboat%20tour%20with%20Original%20Wisconsin%20Ducks.%20Tickets%20felt%20a%20bit%20pricey%2C%20costing%20our%20family%20of%20four%20%24120%2C%20but%20it%20was%20by%20far%20the%20best%20activity%20we%20did.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20War%20II-era%20amphibious%20boat%20to