-purshotam-dhillon-three-indian-origin-men-jailed-in-london-for-running-174000-drugs-network%2Farticleshow%2F132051246.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fbikramjit-brar-hardeep-thind-and-purshotam-dhillon-three-indian-origin-men-jailed-in-london-for-running-174000-drugs-network%2Famp_articleshow%2F132051246.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fbikramjit-brar-hardeep-thind-and-purshotam-dhillon-three-indian-origin-men-jailed-in-london-for-running-174000-drugs-network%2Famp_articleshow%2F132051246.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%2012-year-old%20son%20suggested%20we%20take%20the%20scenic%20route.%20It's%20helped%20us%20appreciate%20our%20town%2C%20and%20he's%20opened%20up%20to%20us%20more%20in%20the%20car.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222398%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20son.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d5661e218c3b62535d1e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222215%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20son%20suggested%20taking%20a%20more%20scenic%20route%20to%20school.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ashley%20Archambault%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20sharing%20a%20car%20while%20we%20save%20up%20for%20another.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERecently%2C%20my%2012-year-old%20son%20suggested%20we%20take%20a%20more%20scenic%20route%20to%20school.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESurprisingly%2C%20it%20didn't%20take%20much%20longer%2C%20and%20it's%20gotten%20us%20all%20talking%20more%20in%20the%20car.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsharing-car-with-partner-saving-money-challenges-benefits-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esharing%20one%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20summer%20while%20we%20save%20up%20for%20a%20second%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20opting%20to%20take%20the%20scenic%20route%20for%20trips%20around%20town.%20We%20can%20actually%20credit%20our%2012-year-old%20son%20for%20the%20change%2C%20who%20requested%20we%20start%20taking%20a%20different%20way%20to%20school%20in%20the%20morning%20%E2%80%94%20one%20through%20town%2C%20on%20side%20roads%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20OK%20with%20the%20change%20as%20long%20as%20the%20drive%20didn't%20take%20too%20much%20longer.%20My%20husband%20compared%20the%20two%20routes%20on%20Google%20Maps%2C%20and%20we%20were%20all%20surprised%20to%20discover%20that%20the%20scenic%20route%20only%20took%20one%20minute%20longer.%20No%20one%20minded%20leaving%20the%20house%20a%20minute%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20avoid%20the%20highway%2C%20so%20we%20tried%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223091d444-08af-49bc-9044-d6781c6601d7%5C%22%3EAfter%20testing%20out%20the%20scenic%20route%20just%20once%2C%20we%20were%20hooked%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20highway%20speeds%20are%20enough%20to%20make%20me%20grip%20the%20wheel%20tighter%2C%20and%20I%20know%20our%20son%20can%20feel%20that%20kind%20of%20energy%20shift%20in%20the%20car.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-drivers-license-16-teenagers-parents-carpool-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20driver%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20need%20to%20focus%20solely%20on%20the%20road%2C%20and%20even%20when%20I'm%20in%20the%20passenger%20seat%2C%20I%20keep%20my%20eyes%20straight%20ahead.%20When%20I%20shared%20this%20with%20my%20husband%2C%20he%20said%20he%20felt%20similar%20in%20that%20it%20is%20far%20more%20draining%20to%20take%20the%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20experimenting%20with%20other%20routes%20to%20our%20most%20frequent%20destinations%20and%20found%20that%20the%20time%20difference%20was%20about%20the%20same%20for%20nearly%20all%20of%20them.%20If%20we're%20just%20going%20somewhere%20nearby%2C%20it%20often%20takes%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20time%20to%20get%20there%20via%20the%20more%20scenic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20much%20more%20relaxing%20%E2%80%94%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20husband%20and%20son%20in%20the%20car.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d569ba25092c74cc9f3f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222363%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20finds%20that%20conversations%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20son%20in%20the%20car%20have%20improved.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ashley%20Archambault%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d92a4ff-7291-42c2-8dbb-58c54075f394%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20more%20beautiful%20way%20has%20helped%20me%20feel%20more%20grateful%20for%20where%20we%20live%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20pointing%20out%20how%20lucky%20we%20are%20to%20be%20driving%20along%20the%20coast%20in%20our%20Florida%20town%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20any%20of%20us%20to%20start%20taking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbackyard-trends-popular-out-of-style-designers-gardeners-landscapers-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20own%20backyard%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20granted.%20After%20sharing%20this%20with%20another%20local%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20one%20of%20our%20favorite%20routes%20is%20actually%20designated%20as%20the%20Indian%20River%20Lagoon%20National%20Scenic%20Byway%2C%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20an%20alternative%20to%20taking%20the%20highway%20to%20admire%20our%20natural%20Florida%20landscape.%20It%20starts%20just%20north%20of%20where%20we%20live%20in%20Titusville%2C%20Florida%2C%20and%20runs%20almost%20250%20miles%20down%20along%20the%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20a%20small%20town%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20nature%20sanctuaries%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20us%20to%20see%20all%20kinds%20of%20wildlife.%20My%20husband%20also%20loves%20driving%20through%20the%20main%20streets%20in%20town%2C%20admiring%20the%20architecture%2C%20and%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fthe-best-indoor-herb-garden%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20and%20gardening%20ideas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20even%20learn%20about%20upcoming%20events%20around%20town%20from%20the%20signs%20we%20see%20when%20we're%20out.%20All%20of%20these%20things%20boost%20our%20mood%20and%20give%20us%20a%20lot%20to%20start%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288f3f18c-75b1-4274-aa05-0e51e51bbe2c%5C%22%3EThe%20scenery%20helps%20us%20get%20the%20conversation%20going%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20noticing%20that%20we%20were%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-conversations-tween-car-rides-to-school-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etalking%20more%20during%20drives%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20then%20I%20realized%20that%20our%20preteen%20son%20was%20opening%20up%20more%20with%20us%20in%20the%20car%3B%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20few%20times%20our%20son%20really%20starts%20talking%20these%20days.%20Adding%20one%20more%20minute%20to%20our%20drives%20sometimes%20feels%20like%20a%20bonus%20just%20to%20hear%20him%20talk%20a%20little%20more%20and%20learn%20about%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20eliminating%20the%20stress%20we'd%20otherwise%20be%20under%20on%20the%20highway%20and%20with%20so%20much%20more%20to%20see%20along%20the%20way%2C%20the%20family%20conversations%20we've%20been%20having%20in%20the%20car%20have%20become%20much%20more%20meaningful.%20Even%20when%20it's%20just%20me%20and%20my%20husband%20%E2%80%94%20or%20me%20and%20my%20son%20%E2%80%94%20the%20effect%20is%20the%20same.%20We%20just%20talk%20more%20overall%20when%20we%20take%20the%20scenic%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20more%20relaxing%20way%20together%20has%20been%20the%20unexpected%20life%20hack%20that%20got%20our%20whole%20family%20talking%20again%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3C