6quot%3BIt's%20me.%20I'm%20not%20good%20enough%2C%20and%20I'm%20never%20going%20to%20find%20a%20job%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20ago%2C%20I%20said%20we%20were%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-navigate-toughest-job-market-apply-for-jobs-last-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworst%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20I'd%20seen%20in%20my%2010%20years%20as%20a%20career%20coach.%20This%20year%20feels%20worse.%20It's%20not%20just%20more%20people%20competing%20for%20fewer%20roles%3B%20job%20seekers%20are%20sifting%20through%20scams%2C%20creating%20personal%20brands%2C%20getting%20referrals%2C%20and%20going%20through%20six%20rounds%20of%20interviews%2C%20only%20to%20get%20ghosted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20get%20hired%20using%20a%20unique%20hack%2C%20strategy%2C%20or%20tactic%3F%20If%20you're%20comfortable%20discussing%20it%20with%20a%20reporter%2C%20please%20fill%20out%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FQKxdZMsWLpYmKWBQ7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider%20wants%20to%20hear%20from%20people%20who've%20cracked%20the%20job%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20with%20a%20bold%20or%20unconventional%20approach%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-hired-in-month-by-making-personalized-decks-heres-how-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esending%20personalized%20slide%20decks%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20place%20of%20cover%20letters%2C%20treating%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftreated-job-like-sales-cycle-landed-new-role-two-months-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20hunt%20like%20a%20sales%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffound-new-job-within-two-months-of-layoff-notice-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5%20specific%20tricks%3C%2Fa%3E%20