Fukraine-strikes-major-russian-oil-refinery-in-drone-barrage-two-killed%2Famp_articleshow%2F132050217.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seychelles%2C%20India%20seek%20a%20world%20where%20development%20is%20more%20inclusive%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782645984000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fseychelles-india-seek-a-world-where-development-is-more-inclusive-pm-modi-126062800475_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Addressing%20the%20National%20Assembly%20of%20Seychelles%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20reaffirmed%20India's%20commitment%20to%20climate%20justice%2C%20inclusive%20development%20and%20deeper%20bilateral%20ties%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A90%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20graduated%20debt-free%2C%20but%20my%20husband%20had%20%2420K%20in%20student%20loans.%20Here's%20what%20we%20want%20our%20kids%20to%20know%20about%20taking%20out%20loans%20for%20college.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222851%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20author%20with%20her%20family%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ebce0360acd489560c05e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222138%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20graduated%20from%20college%20without%20any%20student%20loan%20debt.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kris%20Ann%20Valdez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20graduated%20debt-free%20by%20earning%20scholarships%2C%20going%20to%20school%20close%20to%20home%2C%20and%20working.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20had%20student%20loans%2C%20and%20we%20want%20our%20kids%20to%20avoid%20taking%20out%20student%20loans.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20care%20more%20about%20my%20kids%20not%20going%20into%20debt%20than%20where%20they%20go%20to%20college.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%2014%2C%20I%20overheard%20my%20parents%20say%20they%20would%20not%20be%20paying%20for%20their%20kids%20to%20attend%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolleges-highest-earning-graduates-every-state%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efour-year%20university%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20any%20of%20us%20wanted%20the%20traditional%20college%20experience%2C%20we'd%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20pay%20for%20it%20ourselves.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-students-should-consider-community-college-benefits-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECommunity%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20always%20an%20option%2C%20and%20they'd%20let%20us%20live%20at%20home%20while%20going%20to%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20oldest%20kid%2C%20I%20remember%20feeling%20stunned%20at%20first.%20For%20many%20of%20my%20friends%2C%20college%20was%20treated%20like%20an%20automatic%20next%20step%20that%20parents%20somehow%20financed.%20But%20after%20the%20disappointment%20wore%20off%2C%20it%20lit%20a%20fire%20in%20me.%20I%20threw%20myself%20into%20academics%2C%20determined%20to%20earn%20scholarships%20large%20enough%20to%20make%20my%20four-year%20university%20dreams%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20finished%20high%20school%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Fbest-scholarship-websites%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull-ride%20academic%20scholarship%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20any%20in-state%20university.%20But%20since%20my%20scholarship%20didn't%20include%20housing%2C%20I%20chose%20the%20least%20glamorous%20option%20by%20attending%20the%20school%20closest%20to%20home.%20I%20commuted%20to%20class%2C%20nannied%2C%20overloaded%20credits%20every%20semester%2C%20including%20summers%2C%20and%20gratefully%20accepted%20the%20%242%2C000%20a%20year%20my%20parents%20offered%20toward%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMostly%20living%20on%20peanut%20butter%20and%20jelly%20sandwiches%20and%20praying%20my%20debit%20card%20had%20enough%20money%20to%20fill%20up%20my%20gas%20tank%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrad-school-midlife-career-change-debt-free-side-gig-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egraduated%20debt-free%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20three%20years.%20My%20younger%20siblings%20each%20found%20their%20own%20version%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bscrappy%26quot%3B%20route%2C%20too.%20My%20sister%20started%20community%20college%20classes%20at%2015.%20My%20brother%20launched%20a%20business%20as%20a%20teenager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22471e6a49-b6cc-4c58-8b0b-7a83d5abf5fb%5C%22%3EWatching%20other%20people's%20choices%20changed%20how%20I%20viewed%20college%20debt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20married%20someone%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-education-department-cuts-new-report-trump-repayment-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudent%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20many%20other%20borrowers%2C%20my%20husband's%20debt%20load%20was%20actually%20modest%2C%20around%20%2420%2C000%2C%20but%20in%20our%20early%20years%20of%20marriage%2C%20even%20that%20felt%20overwhelming.%20Every%20time%20we%20deferred%20the%20loans%2C%20the%20interest%20just%20kept%20on%20accruing.%20So%20we%20took%20on%20side%20hustles%20to%20pay%20them%20off%20faster%2C%20working%20weddings%20and%20bar%20mitzvahs%20and%20proctoring%20ACT%20tests%20on%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20watched%20several%20friends%20without%20degrees%20out-earn%20many%20college%20graduates%20because%20they%20had%20entered%20the%20workforce%20earlier%20and%20developed%20entrepreneurial%20skills.%20Fortunately%20for%20them%2C%20they%20weren't%20weighed%20down%20by%20student%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20dawned%20on%20me%20that%20the%20narrative%20that%20going%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-college-still-worth-it-tech-execs-kids-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollege%20equals%20success%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20black-and-white%20view%20of%20life%20that's%20not%20always%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272c8420b-5382-4d35-897c-4e14a3b37369%5C%22%3EWorking%20in%20admissions%20further%20made%20me%20rethink%20the%20%26quot%3Bdream%20school%26quot%3B%20mentality%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20both%20worked%20as%20university%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-admissions-counselor-looks-for-soft-skills-application-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadmissions%20counselors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20we%20watched%20families%20willingly%20take%20on%20staggering%20amounts%20of%20debt%20in%20pursuit%20of%20their%20child's%20university%20dream.%20Some%20shrugged%20off%20six-figure%20loan%20amounts%20as%20though%20it%20was%20simply%20the%20unavoidable%20cost%20of%20giving%20their%20children%20the%20%26quot%3Bfull%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20often%20walked%20away%20from%20meetings%20worried%20that%20students%20didn't%20understand%20the%20long-term%20choices%20they%20were%20making.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20developed%20a%20slogan%20we%20used%20to%20advise%20our%20students%3A%20graduate%20college%20in%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20time%20possible%20with%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20only%20way%20we%20could%20ethically%20keep%20doing%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229eb8bcd2-d11a-4992-90a0-845eeed447d9%5C%22%3EWhy%20we%20won't%20fully%20fund%20our%20children's%20college%20educations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20parents%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20in%20agreement%20that%20we%20will%20not%20pay%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20for%20our%20children%20to%20attend%20a%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20value%20education%2C%20but%20we%20also%20value%20financial%20freedom.%20If%20one%20of%20our%20children%20wants%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-colleges-highest-earning-graduates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20earning%20potential%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20requires%20extensive%20schooling%2C%20that's%20one%20thing.%20But%20we%20don't%20believe%20an%2018-year-old%20should%20casually%20take%20on%20%24100%2C000%20in%20debt%20for%20a%20career%20path%20that%20may%20never%20realistically%20allow%20them%20to%20repay%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20invest%20time%20in%20helping%20my%20kids%20navigate%20the%20scholarship%20process%2C%20educating%20them%20on%20how%20student%20loans%20work%2C%20and%20asking%20them%20to%20review%20all%20the%20options%20to%20determine%20what's%20best%20for%20their%20needs%20%E2%80%94%20this%20might%20mean%20attending%20community%20college%2C%20going%20to%20trade%20school%2C%20or%20entering%20the%20workforce%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20path%20my%20children%20choose%2C%20I%20just%20hope%20they%20walk%20away%20from%20our%20home%20understanding%20that%20sometimes%20the%20easier%20or%20more%20glamorous%20path%20comes%20with%20the%20hardest%20long-term%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgraduated-college-debt-free-want-kids-avoid-student-loans-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782645661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ebce0360acd489560c05e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgraduated-college-debt-free-want-kids-avoid-student-loans-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20had%20%2420%2C000%20in%20student%20loan%20debt%2C%20while%20I%20graduated%20debt-free.%20I%20care%20more%20about%20my%20kids%20avoiding%20debt%20than%20where%20they%20go%20to%20college.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kris%20Ann%20Valdez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20left%20Google%20after%20making%20nearly%20%241M%20in%20a%20year.%20Fears%20about%20layoffs%20and%20missing%20out%20on%20the%20AI%20boom%20gave%20me%20the%20push.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221439%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yousuf%20Imran%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3e87f3360acd489560bc77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221079%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYousuf%20Imran%20left%20Google%20in%20April%20to%20start%20an%20AI%20company%20after%20earning%20nearly%20%241%20million%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EYousuf%20Imran%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EYousuf%20Imran%20earned%20nearly%20%241%20million%20at%20Google%20before%20leaving%20to%20start%20an%20AI%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20%26quot%3BAI%20FOMO%26quot%3B%20helped%20convince%20him%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-big-tech-watching-middle-managers-struggle-2025-10%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleave%20Big%20Tech%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EImran%20shared%20how%20he%20prepared%20financially%20before%20betting%20on%20himself.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Yousuf%20Imran%2C%20a%2041-year-old%20former%20account%20executive%20at%20Google%20based%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20earned%20nearly%20%241%20million%20last%20year%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-landed-role-google-viral-video-laid-off-how-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaccount%20executive%20at%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20some%20%26quot%3BFOMO%26quot%3B%20around%20the%20AI%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20most%20people%20at%20Google%20would%20tell%20you%20the%20same%20if%20they%20were%20being%20candid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20pays%20very%20well%2C%20but%20the%20equity%20packages%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-everybody-wants-to-work-at-anthropic-or-openai-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20in%20a%20different%20universe.%20A%20three-%20or%20four-year%20stock%20grant%20at%20one%20of%20these%20companies%20can%20be%20life-changing%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20math%20was%20part%20of%20my%20own%20calculus%20in%20deciding%20to%20start%20my%20own%20business%20focused%20on%20AI%20sales%20tools.%20If%20the%20only%20way%20to%20get%20real%20upside%20in%20this%20AI%20moment%20is%20equity%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20you%20ask%20yourself%20whether%20the%20equity%20should%20be%20in%20your%20own%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d21f3c2e-08c0-4945-86e8-b5c769704eaf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20I%20built%20a%20million-dollar%20sales%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20Queens%20and%20got%20into%20sales%20because%20it's%20a%20profession%20where%20talent%20can%20outrun%20credentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20roughly%2015-year%20career%20in%20sales%2C%20I%20joined%20Google%20in%202020%2C%20helping%20customers%20solve%20business%20problems%20using%20Google's%20AI%20and%20machine-learning%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20base%20salary%20last%20year%20was%20roughly%20%24170%2C000%2C%20but%20commissions%20made%20up%20the%20majority%20of%20my%20compensation.%20My%20W-2%20income%20was%20about%20%24986%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20part%20of%20my%20success%20came%20from%20what%20I%20call%20the%20immigrant%20hustle.%20My%20family%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-new-york-city-biggest-surprises-challenges-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20was%20five%20years%20old%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20I%20grew%20up%20believing%20that%20if%20you%20don't%20put%20in%20the%20work%2C%20you%20won't%20get%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20I%20believe%20my%20curiosity%20differentiated%20me.%20I%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20learning%20about%20my%20customers'%20businesses%2C%20understanding%20the%20problems%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20solve%2C%20and%20becoming%20deeply%20knowledgeable%20about%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20so%20I%20could%20help%20them%20use%20the%20technology%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20speaking%20with%20workers%20who've%20found%20themselves%20at%20a%20corporate%20crossroads%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20due%20to%20a%20layoff%2C%20resignation%2C%20job%20search%2C%20or%20shifting%20workplace%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShare%20your%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSechTVqVWQve8iqYssNriCXdtwwdgGRixNNZpmslSKBQqIJ8g%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c4213d18-16ab-4e89-9737-02f667664dca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20became%20more%20than%20my%20day%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20my%20interest%20in%20AI%20went%20beyond%20my%20work%20at%20Google.%20While%20I%20was%20selling%20AI%20products%20during%20the%20day%2C%20I%20was%20spending%20nights%20and%20weekends%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-workers-learning-ai-tools-after-work-productivity-jobs-amazon-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexperimenting%20with%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20ChatGPT%2C%20Claude%2C%20and%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20building%20small%20projects%20for%20myself.%20Since%20I'm%20not%20a%20software%20developer%20by%20trade%2C%20I'd%20talk%20to%20multiple%20AI%20tools%20to%20try%20to%20figure%20things%20out%20and%2C%20after%20some%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20get%20a%20win.%20Vibe%20coding%20felt%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20video%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20tools%20improved%2C%20those%20projects%20became%20more%20ambitious.%20I%20built%20several%20apps%20and%20side%20projects%20over%20a%20roughly%20year-and-a-half%20period%20and%20began%20thinking%20seriously%20about%20the%20opportunity%20to%20start%20my%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20thought%20about%20my%20job%20security%20at%20Google%2C%20given%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-clouds-quiet-layoffs-hit-cybersecurity-teams-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20company's%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20prior%20years.%20What%20struck%20me%20about%20the%20recent%20layoff%20rounds%20at%20Google%20was%20that%20they%20hit%20genuinely%20talented%20people.%20The%20uncertainty%20of%20a%20potential%20layoff%20was%20another%20input%20into%20my%20decision%20to%20bet%20on%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20six%20years%20after%20joining%20Google%2C%20I%20left%20Google%20to%20found%20Mangosteen%20Studio%2C%20an%20AI%20product%20lab%20building%20go-to-market%20tooling%20for%20account%20executives.%20The%20thesis%20is%20simple%3A%20I%20spent%2020%20years%20quota-carrying%20at%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20companies%2C%20so%20I'm%20building%20the%20tools%20I%20wish%20I'd%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbb1eba7-f578-4deb-aaa0-86bfbac05148%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20prepared%20financially%20before%20taking%20the%20leap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeaving%20Google%20wasn't%20something%20I%20did%20impulsively.%20Google%20is%20a%20vast%20organization%20with%20incredible%20resources%20and%20teams%20working%20on%20bleeding-edge%20AI.%20Losing%20that%20%26quot%3Binsider%26quot%3B%20access%20and%20being%20less%20visible%20in%20that%20world%20was%20a%20major%20point%20of%20hesitation%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20financial%20considerations%2C%20particularly%20making%20sure%20I%20had%20enough%20savings%20to%20give%20the%20business%20a%20real%20chance%20without%20having%20to%20make%20major%20changes%20to%20my%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20set%20aside%20%24200%2C000%20to%20fund%20the%20business%20for%20two%20years%20and%20another%20%24150%2C000%20to%20cover%20my%20mortgage%20and%20personal%20expenses%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20primary%20goal%20is%20to%20bootstrap%20the%20business%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%20and%20not%20feel%20pressured%20to%20raise%20money%2C%20because%20investors%20quickly%20take%20your%20equity.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20be%20comfortable%20enough%20financially%20to%20focus%20on%20building%20the%20business%20rather%20than%20worrying%20about%20paying%20my%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22652c9295-b9a7-41ca-90d8-ac579c3cc1e5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20is%20changing%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I'm%20running%20the%20company%20as%20a%20solo%20founder%20with%20a%20small%20team%20of%20engineers%2C%20marketers%2C%20and%20other%20contractors.%20It's%20still%20early%2C%20but%20many%20sales%20professionals%20have%20already%20used%20our%20AI%20tools%20free%20of%20charge%2C%20which%20has%20given%20me%20confidence%20that%20we're%20building%20something%20people%20find%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20who%20feel%20stuck%20in%20their%20careers%20or%20aren't%20being%20challenged%2C%20AI%20is%20giving%20people%20an%20opportunity%20to%20build%20something%20of%20their%20own.%20The%20key%20is%20having%20domain%20expertise%20you%20can%20lean%20on.%20I%20wasn't%20a%20software%20engineer%2C%20but%20I%20spent%2020%20years%20learning%20the%20problems%20salespeople%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20I%20recognized%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-podcaster-quit-ai-tech-startup-job-market-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleaving%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20meant%20leaving%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20behind%20%E2%80%94%20both%20financially%20and%20professionally.%20But%20my%20confidence%20and%20domain%20expertise%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20this%20was%20the%20right%20moment%20to%20take%20the%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20via%20Signal%20at%20jzinkula.29.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employee-made-one-million-explains-why-left-big-tech2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782645356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3e87eb360acd489560bc74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employee-made-one-million-explains-why-left-big-tech2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20Google%20employee%20says%20AI%20equity%2C%20job%20security%20concerns%2C%20and%20years%20of%20side%20projects%20convinced%20him%20to%20leave%20and%20build%20his%20own%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20tale%20of%20two%20photographs%3A%20Palestinian%20journalist's%20images%20capture%20horror%20of%20Israeli%20prisons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782645331000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132049942%2Cimgsize-102896.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fa-tale-of-two-photographs-palestinian-journalists-images-capture-horror-of-israeli-prisons%2Farticleshow%2F132049911.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%