20empty%20nest%20since%20her%20two%20sons%20still%20live%20with%20her.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kimberly%20Witt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20two%20sons%20still%20live%20with%20me%20so%20they%20can%20save%20on%20housing%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20means%20my%20expenses%20have%20gone%20up%2C%20like%20electricity%20and%20grocery%20budgets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20should%20be%20enjoying%20the%20financial%20freedom%20of%20an%20empty%20nest%20now%2C%20but%20I'm%20trying%20to%20adjust.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%2021-year-old%20son%20recently%20accompanied%20me%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-store-ready-to-eat-replacing-restaurants-trends-competition-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrocery%20store%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20list%20wasn't%20lengthy.%20We%20needed%20a%20few%20items%20for%20a%20cookout%20with%20neighbors%3A%20hot%20dogs%2C%20brats%2C%20buns%2C%20some%20fresh%20produce%2C%20and%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20these%20shared%20trips%2C%20the%20two%20of%20us%20have%20taken%20to%20playing%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprice-is-right-bob-barker-models-sexual-harrassment-me-too-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrice%20is%20Right%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B-inspired%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eguessing%20game.%20Who%20can%20correctly%20estimate%20the%20final%20total%20without%20going%20over%3F%20He's%20uncannily%20good%20at%20this%20game%2C%20beating%20me%20nearly%20every%20time%2C%20often%20guessing%20within%20a%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20%2480.78%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20whispered%20as%20the%20Aldi%20checker%20stacked%20our%20items%20in%20the%20basket.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I'll%20say%20%2477.35%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%2492.17%2C%26quot%3B%20our%20checker%20stated.%20He%20won%20our%20game%2C%20but%20the%20victory%20was%20bittersweet%20because%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20never%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20move%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20son%20lamented%2C%20a%20hint%20of%20a%20joke%20in%20his%20voice%20as%20we%20packed%20up%20our%20groceries.%20But%20we%20both%20knew%20there%20was%20some%20seriousness%20to%20his%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275beab8e-ca53-40a8-a057-ec2f3a8d9cb1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20two%20adult%20sons%20moved%20back%20in%20to%20save%20money%20on%20housing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%2021-year-old%20just%20moved%20back%20into%20his%20childhood%20bedroom%20in%20May%20after%20being%20out%20on%20his%20own.%20He'd%20been%20subleasing%20a%20shared%20apartment%20and%20managing%20his%20other%20social%20expenses%2C%20but%20ultimately%20decided%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20pay%20rent.%20While%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadopted-kids-ethiopia-saved-college-tuition-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprioritize%20tuition%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20our%20two%20young%20adult%20sons%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20the%20disposable%20income%20to%20cover%20all%20their%20living%20expenses.%20Unwilling%20to%20accrue%20debt%20just%20to%20live%20near%20campus%2C%20he%20chose%20to%20come%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20under%20our%20roof%20making%20that%20calculation.%20His%20older%20brother%20opted%20to%20attend%20a%20nearby%20college%20specifically%20to%20save%20on%20housing%2C%20so%20now%20we%20have%20both%20sons%20living%20at%20home%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20St.%20Paul%2C%20Minnesota%2C%20across%20the%20river%20from%20Minneapolis%2C%20where%20housing%20prices%20are%20considered%20%26quot%3Baffordable%26quot%3B%20when%20compared%20to%20other%20major%20cities.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apartments.com%2Frent-market-trends%2Fminneapolis-mn%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApartments.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20average%20studio%20costs%20%241%2C424%20a%20month.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac31bf1c-4743-40bb-9de6-b07e48417dfb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20sons%20aren't%20failing%20to%20launch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20nationwide%20trend.%20We%20have%20friends%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-young-adults-explain-why-moved-back-in-with-parents-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollege%20graduates%3C%2Fa%3E%20moved%20back%20home%20to%20hunt%20for%20jobs%2C%20and%20other%20friends%20whose%20daughter%20and%20her%20husband%20live%20in%20their%20basement%20as%20they%20save%20for%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20their%20first%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20sons%2C%20a%20part-time%20student%20job%20just%20didn't%20provide%20enough%20income%20to%20justify%20exorbitant%20rent%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20decided%20that%20as%20long%20as%20our%20sons%20are%20full-time%20students%2C%20they%20can%20continue%20to%20live%20at%20home%20with%20few%20expenses.%20They%20both%20chip%20in%20to%20put%20gas%20in%20the%20family%20cars%2C%20but%20we%20foot%20the%20bill%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20household%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5fa52d3-d34d-4c28-988e-5e75ff9605b5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20my%20expenses%20have%20increased%20as%20a%20result%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20proud%20my%20sons%20are%20savvy%20with%20their%20hard-earned%20money%2C%20having%20them%20both%20back%20home%20for%20a%20season%20means%20our%20expenses%20have%20increased.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20realizing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-financial-independence-fire-movement-investing-saving-early-retirement-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%20associated%20with%20an%20empty%20nest%20won't%20be%20our%20reality%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20adults%20living%20at%20home%20means%20increased%20utility%20bills.%20The%20lights%20are%20on%20more.%20More%20water%20is%20needed%20for%20showers%2C%20laundry%2C%20and%20the%20dishwasher.%20We%20had%20an%20earlier-than-expected%20heatwave%20here%20in%20Minnesota%2C%20so%20the%20air%20conditioner%20has%20been%20running%20more%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-produce-prices-rising-oil-soars-during-war-with-iran-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrocery%20bills%20are%20higher%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too%2C%20and%20not%20just%20because%20of%20war%2C%20tariffs%2C%20and%20inflation.%20When%20my%20son%20lived%20on%20his%20own%2C%20he%20often%20ate%20a%20small%20breakfast%2C%20skipped%20lunch%2C%20and%20planned%20cheap%20dinners%20like%20eggs%20and%20toast.%20That's%20changed%20now%20that%20we're%20buying%20groceries.%20Long%20gone%20are%20the%20days%20of%20satisfying%20the%20family%20of%20four%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20boxes%20of%20macaroni%20and%20cheese%20or%20grilled%20cheese%20sandwiches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20recent%20trip%20to%20Aldi%2C%20we%20spent%20nearly%20%2420%20on%20chicken%20that%20would%20last%20a%20couple%20of%20dinners.%20While%20that's%20considerably%20less%20than%20what%20we%20would%20spend%20going%20out%2C%20it's%20also%20way%20more%20than%20I%20would%20be%20spending%20on%20dinners%20of%20cereal%20and%20popcorn%20if%20our%20sons%20weren't%20home.%20I%20primarily%20shop%20at%20Aldi%20because%20of%20their%20lower%20prices%2C%20but%20even%20those%20prices%20add%20up%20for%20twenty-somethings%20focused%20on%20weightlifting%2C%20clean%20eating%2C%20and%20prioritizing%20protein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236bdfdb6-5a80-4cbc-9d5c-1e0bf5e7fc54%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20what%20the%20future%20holds%20for%20our%20family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20our%20young%20adult%20sons%20continue%20to%20live%20here%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-grads-class-of-2026-job-searching-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eafter%20graduation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20packing%20a%20lunch%20before%20heading%20out%20to%20their%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they%20can%20find%20those%20jobs%3F%20What%20kinds%20of%20parameters%20will%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20establish%20if%20that%20time%20comes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%2C%20so%20for%20now%20I%20will%20try%20to%20relax%20into%20this%20season%20as%20much%20as%20I%20can%2C%20enjoying%20the%20shared%20meals%20and%20chaotic%20mornings%20as%20everyone%20heads%20out%20to%20summer%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20need%20me%2C%20I'll%20be%20over%20here%20researching%20economical%20protein%20sources%20and%20water-saving%20showerheads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadult-sons-moved-back-in-expenses-increase-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782644821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3dd42aa25092c74cc9f861%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadult-sons-moved-back-in-expenses-increase-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20two%20sons%20still%20live%20with%20me%20so%20they%20can%20save%20on%20housing%20costs.%20That%20means%20my%20expenses%20have%20gone%20up%2C%20like%20electricity%20and%20grocery%20budgets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kimberly%20Witt)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20Harry%20may%20cancel%20upcoming%20UK%20visit%20with%20Meghan%2C%20children%20after%20security%20setback%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782644119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132049601%2Cimgsize-82730.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprince-harry-may-cancel-uk-visit-with-meghan-children-after-being-denied-police-protec