over%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20story%20had%20our%20newsroom%20buzzing%20this%20past%20week%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslate-ev-pickup-starting-price-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20surprisingly%20low%20price%20for%20the%20tiny%20electric%20truck%20backed%20by%20Jeff%20Bezos%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlate%20Auto%20revealed%20its%20base-model%2C%20two-seater%20would%20cost%20%2424%2C950%2C%20branding%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20affordable%20truck%20in%20America.%26quot%3B%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20hit%20US%20roads%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20exactly%20does%20Slate%20keep%20the%20price%20so%20low%3F%20By%20stripping%20away%20many%20of%20the%20features%20that%20drivers%20have%20come%20to%20expect.%20There's%20no%20touchscreen%20or%20built-in%20stereo.%20The%20windows%20operate%20with%20old-school%20manual%20cranks.%20Its%20estimated%20range%20tops%20out%20at%20just%20205%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20truck%20is%20tiny%2C%20too.%20At%20just%2014.5%20feet%20long%2C%20the%20vehicle%20is%20closer%20in%20size%20to%20a%20Toyota%20Camry%20than%20a%20Ford%20F-150.%20The%20driver's%20seat%20is%20low%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20more%20like%20a%20sedan%20than%20an%20SUV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20tag%20is%20undeniably%20attractive%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20new%20cars%20seem%20to%20only%20get%20more%20expensive.%20Fewer%20than%205%25%20of%20new%20vehicles%20sold%20last%20year%20had%20starting%20prices%20under%20%2425%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20car-shopping%20website%20Edmunds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20wasn't%20the%20price%20that%20divided%20our%20newsroom%3B%20it%20was%20the%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20colleague%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ugliest%20thing%20I'd%20ever%20seen.%26quot%3B%20Another%20said%20they'd%20happily%20buy%20one.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fdan-defrancesco%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDan%20DeFrancesco%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20newsletter's%20weekday%20writer%2C%20was%20also%20a%20fan%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20this%20country%20was%20built%20on%20excess.%20(And%20God%20knows%20I%20love%20an%20all-you-can-eat%20sushi%20spot.)%20But%20less%20is%20more%20with%20pick-up%20trucks.%20Unless%20you%20have%20a%20professional%20need%20for%20it%2C%20owning%20anything%20bigger%20than%20a%20Ford%20F-150%20just%20makes%20you%20a%20hardo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEV%20demand%20has%20cooled%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20making%20it%20a%20tough%20time%20for%20Slate%20to%20come%20to%20market.%20Still%2C%20one%20of%20its%20main%20selling%20points%20is%20its%20level%20of%20customization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20says%20it%20will%20offer%20more%20than%20200%20accessories%20and%20add-ons%2C%20including%20vehicle%20wraps%2C%20seat%20covers%2C%20roof%20racks%2C%20light%20covers%2C%20a%20stereo%2C%20and%20interior%20tech.%20BI's%20Ben%20Shimkus%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslates-ev-truck-tiny-customizable-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20detailed%20overview%20of%20all%20the%20add-ons%20and%20their%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20take%3A%20At%20first%20glance%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20truck%20was%20ugly.%20But%20after%20playing%20around%20on%20the%20website%20with%20accessories%2C%20colors%2C%20and%20designs%2C%20the%20concept%20grew%20on%20me.%20There%20is%20also%20something%20quaint%20about%20an%20old-school%20design%20without%20all%20the%20bells%20and%20whistles%20found%20in%20today's%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslate-truck-affordability-comfort-tradeoff-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyou%20can't%20beat%20the%20price%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhat%20do%20you%20think%20about%20Slate's%20new%20EV%20truck%3F%20Would%20you%20buy%20one%3F%20Drop%20me%20your%20thoughts%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asrus