rriage%2C%20and%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%2C%20which%20had%20consumed%20many%20of%20his%20own%20friends.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20small%20effort%20grew%20into%20the%20OSCAR%20(Organization%20for%20Social%20Change%2C%20Awareness%20and%20Responsibility)%20Foundation%20in%202010%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20that%20today%20has%20touched%20thousands%20of%20young%20lives%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20lives%20is%20that%20of%20Yamini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20rainy%20afternoon%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20a%20shy%20Class%209%20student%20walked%20nervously%20into%20a%20ground%20where%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation%20had%20gathered%20children.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496964%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShe%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20sure%20if%20football%20was%20her%20game.%20But%20when%20the%20coach%20handed%20her%20a%20ball%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20kick%20it%20away%20from%20yourself%20and%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20something%20changed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20football%20is%20no%20longer%20just%20a%20sport%20for%20Yamini%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ground%20has%20become%20her%20%E2%80%9Csecond%20home%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20rule%20that%20changed%20everything%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYamini%20studies%20in%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20has%20always%20enjoyed%20going%20to%20class.%20Yet%20her%20idea%20of%20education%20changed%20when%20she%20joined%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation.%20Its%20strict%20rule%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CNo%20School%2C%20No%20Football%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20taught%20her%20that%20passion%20and%20discipline%20must%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20foundation%20enforces%20a%20%E2%80%9CNo%20School%2C%20No%20Football%E2%80%9D%20rule%2C%20linking%20access%20to%20football%20training%20to%20consistent%20school%20attendance.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-497017%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20foundation%20enforces%20a%20%E2%80%9CNo%20School%2C%20No%20Football%E2%80%9D%20rule%2C%20linking%20access%20to%20football%20training%20to%20consistent%20school%20attendance.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20many%20kids%20thought%20that%20if%20they%20were%20good%20at%20football%2C%20studies%20didn%E2%80%99t%20matter.%20But%20OSCAR%20showed%20us%20that%20school%20is%20our%20first%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20encouragement%2C%20Yamini%20never%20thought%20of%20dropping%20out.%20Still%2C%20relatives%20and%20neighbours%20often%20questioned%20her%20choices%3A%20%E2%80%9CShe%E2%80%99s%20a%20girl.%20What%20future%20does%20she%20have%20in%20football%3F%20What%20if%20she%20gets%20injured%3F%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20she%20focus%20on%20studies%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Yamini%20laced%20up%20her%20boots%20anyway.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20family%2C%20too%2C%20slowly%20began%20trusting%20the%20process%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20the%20coaches%20at%20OSCAR%20built%20a%20bond%20strong%20enough%20for%20my%20parents%20to%20let%20me%20travel%20alone%20for%20matches%20and%20practice%20in%20Bandra%20or%20Churchgate.%20That%E2%80%99s%20something%20uncommon%20in%20our%20conservative%20neighbourhood%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20dream%20beyond%20the%20neighbourhood%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYamini%E2%80%99s%20football%20journey%20has%20already%20taken%20her%20far.%20She%20captained%20her%20team%20in%20inter-community%20tournaments%2C%20led%20them%20to%20the%20finals%2C%20and%20even%20came%20close%20to%20a%20dream%20%E2%80%94%20trials%20for%20Europe.%20Though%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20beyond%20the%20second%20round%2C%20just%20being%20considered%20filled%20her%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20I%20was%20selected%20for%20Mumbai%20Football%20Association%E2%80%99s%20Luxury%20Football%20Club.%20It%20is%20a%20milestone%20that%20remains%20one%20of%20my%20happiest%20memories%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploa