dia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496559%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%20was%20started%20in%20March%202019%20to%20promote%20planting%20trees%20in%20Punjab%20villages%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPunjab%20is%20not%20just%20a%20state%20to%20me%3B%20it%20is%20a%20breathing%20heritage.%20The%20environmental%20challenges%20we%20face%20are%20not%20isolated%3B%20they%20are%20symptoms%20of%20a%20larger%20disconnect%20between%20communities%20and%20nature.%20Our%20work%20is%20about%20restoring%20that%20bond%2C%20nurturing%20both%20land%20and%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F474029%2Fjagdish-kuniyal-tree-planting-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanting%20trees%20but%20about%20cultivating%20a%20future%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20nature%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20community%20grow%20in%20unison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuiding%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20afforestation%20efforts%20is%20Vishal%20Chowla%2C%20project%20lead%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20rebuild%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20green%20cover%20by%20reintroducing%20native%20tree%20species%20to%20depleted%20landscapes.%20He%20recalls%20the%20early%20days%20vividly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20visited%20these%20villages%2C%20the%20soil%20was%20exhausted%20and%20the%20air%20heavy%20with%20pollution.%20We%20knew%20planting%20trees%20was%20essential%2C%20but%20the%20real%20challenge%20was%20to%20plant%20hope%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20among%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20seed%20of%20hope%20was%20first%20sown%20in%20March%202019%2C%20when%20the%20foundation%20planted%20saplings%20on%20government%20land%20in%20Badaushi%20Kalan%20village.%20It%20was%20a%20modest%20start%2C%20but%20rooted%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20reviving%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20biodiversity%20with%20native%20species%20like%20desi%20beri%2C%20dhaak%2C%20phulai%2C%20and%20farah.%20These%20hardy%20trees%2C%20once%20central%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20natural%20identity%2C%20restore%20soil%20and%20water%20systems%2C%20support%20wildlife%20habitats%2C%20and%20withstand%20climate%20extremes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roundglass%20Foundation%20encourages%20and%20educates%20the%20youth%20to%20plant%20native%20trees%20in%20their%20villages%2C%20so%20that%20the%20initiative%20continues%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496565%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERoundglass%20Foundation%20encourages%20and%20educates%20the%20youth%20to%20plant%20native%20trees%20in%20their%20villages%2C%20so%20that%20the%20initiative%20continues%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20that%20single%20pilot%2C%20the%20project%20has%20spread%20like%20the%20roots%20of%20a%20forest%2C%20reaching%20over%201%2C600%20villages%20with%20more%20than%20three%20million%20native%20trees%20planted.%20The%20model%20is%20as%20much%20social%20as%20it%20is%20environmental.%20TBTP%20stresses%20not%20only%20planting%20but%20also%20long-term%20care.%20Saplings%20are%20nurtured%20for%20up%20to%2030%20months%2C%20creating%20steady%20employment%20for%20local%20residents%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20women%20and%20youth%2C%20who%20make%20up%2070%25%20of%20the%20caregiving%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20happens%20after%20planting%3F%20The%20work%20that%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlanting%20is%20only%20the%20start.%20The%20real%20effort%20is%20in%20the%20care%20%E2%80%94%20watering%2C%20pruning%2C%20and%20protecting%20%E2%80%94%20until%20the%20trees%20can%20stand%20on%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20Gurpreet%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEmpowering%20youth%20through%20this%20work%20is%20important.%20It%20is%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F467221%2Freeva-sood-chemical-free-farming-empower-rural-women-agriva-naturally%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstilling%20purpose%2C%20building%20self-reliance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20reshaping%20how%20communities%20view%20their%20future.%20When%20young%20people%20become%20guardians%20of%20these%20forests%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20they%20lead%20their%20communities%20towards%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Inderjit%20and%20many%20others%2C%20this%20change%20has%20become%20deeply%20personal.%20A%20seasoned%20cultivator%2C%20he%20had%20long%20watched%20his%20soil%20decline.%20He%20offered%20a%20kanal%20of%20his%20private%20land%20to%20the%20project%20with%20cautious%20optimism.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20sceptical%20at%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20tried%20planting%20before%2C%20but%20the%20trees%20didn%E2%80%99t%20survive.%20When%20Roundglass%20came%2C%20they%20stayed%2C%20cared%20for%20the%20saplings%2C%20and%20involved%20us%20in%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20land%20hosts%20a%20flourishing%20mini%20forest%20of%20nearly%20three%20kanals%20with%20over%20700%20trees%20from%20more%20than%20100%20varieties%2C%20including%20peepal%2C%20neem%2C%20and%20jhand.%20The%20impact%20has%20been%20striking.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20diverse%20forest%2C%20resilient%20and%20alive.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F410969%2Fretirement-teacher-turns-barren-hill-thriving-forest-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBirds%20have%20returned%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20crops%20have%20improved%20because%20they%20eat%20the%20pests%20naturally.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20reduced%20chemical%20sprays%2C%20and%20the%20soil%20feels%20richer.%20It%20is%20a%20gift%20to%20the%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20his%20voice%20heavy%20with%20emotion.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20once%20questioned%20why%20I%20was%20so%20involved%20in%20The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project.%20Now%2C%20they%20come%20and%20sit%20in%20the%20forest.%20It%20is%20peaceful%20and%20has%20united%20the%20whole%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBirdsong%20and%20biodiversity%20%E2%80%93%20When%20nature%20returns%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lang%2C%20Romanpreet%20tells%20a%20similar%20story%20of%20renewal.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dry%20patch%20near%20the%20crematorium%20was%20lifeless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20TBTP%20came%20to%20our%20village%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20plant%20trees.%20It%20brought%20work%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20for%20women%20and%20youth%20%E2%80%94%20who%20watered%2C%20tended%2C%20and%20protected%20the%20saplings.%20It%20gave%20us%20purpose%20and%20pride.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20foundation%20has%20planted%20around%20three%20million%20native%20trees%20so%20far%20in%20the%20villages%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496570%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20planted%20around%20three%20million%20native%20trees%20so%20far%20in%20the%20villages%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20what%20was%20barren%20became%20green%20and%20alive.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20see%20prinias%2C%20kingfishers%2C%20coucals%2C%20purple%20sunbirds%2C%20and%20sparrows%20all%20the%20time.%20The%20ecosystem%20is%20healing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20mini%20forests%20are%20not%20isolated%20patches%20but%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20ecological%20strategy.%20Beyond%20shade%20and%20beauty%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F477262%2Fvikrant-tongad-founder-safe-transforms-dumpsite-in-greater-noida-plants-trees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enative%20trees%20conserve%20water%2C%20regenerate%20soil%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20support%20biodiversity.%20Vishal%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrees%20improve%20soil%20moisture%2C%20reduce%20evaporation%2C%20and%20create%20micro-channels%20that%20hold%20rainwater.%20An%20acre%20of%20forest%20can%20save%20over%2012%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20annually%20compared%20to%20conventional%20paddy%20fields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurpreet%20reinforces%20the%20connection%3A%20%E2%80%9CWater%20and%20trees%20are%20intertwined.%20By%20protecting%20one%2C%20we%20safeguard%20the%20other.%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20future%20depends%20on%20this%20balance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20owns%20a%20mini%20forest%3F%20The%20power%20of%20local%20pride%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20balance%20is%20being%20rebuilt%20not%20through%20imposition%20but%20collaboration.%20Much%20of%20the%20land%20is%20government-owned%2C%20but%20when%20individuals%20like%20Inderjit%20offer%20private%20land%2C%20it%20fosters%20co-ownership%20and%20responsibility.%20%E2%80%9CVillages%20take%20ownership%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20survival%20rates%20of%20trees%20are%20so%20high%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20places%2C%20schools%20are%20involved%2C%20turning%20forests%20into%20living%20classrooms%20where%20children%20learn%20about%20ecology%20and%20conservation.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20see%20the%20trees%20grow%20and%20learn%20to%20respect%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Inderjit%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20plants%20seeds%20of%20awareness%20that%20will%20last%20generations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20planting%20a%20few%20saplings%20in%20one%20village%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20statewide%20movement%20spanning%2017%20districts.%20Each%20of%20the%20three%20million%20trees%20has%20been%20carefully%20tracked%2C%20with%20survival%20rates%20monitored%20through%20rigorous%20documentation%20and%20local%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-500x375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20native%20trees%20help%20to%20use%20water%20wisely%20and%20improve%