start%20at%20Rs%203%2C500%2C%20while%20customised%20versions%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%209%2C500%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECouples%20can%20choose%20not%20just%20the%20colours%20and%20flowers%2C%20but%20also%20add%20small%20personal%20details.%20%E2%80%9COne%20couple%20wanted%20their%20college%20colours%20included%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20fell%20in%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20beauty%20of%20crochet%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20saving%20flowers%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saving%20a%20moment%2C%20a%20story%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20love%20stitched%20by%20hand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F475664%2Fsustainability-mafia-students-climate-startups-climate-solutions-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESustainability%20%3C%2Fa%3Eplays%20a%20role%20here%20too.%20Manya%20prefers%20cotton%20yarn%20for%20its%20lightness%20and%20comfort%2C%20and%20she%20often%20upcycles%20beads%20or%20embellishments%20from%20old%20jewellery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20has%20been%20her%20biggest%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20by%20posting%20crochet%20work%20online.%20Consistency%2C%20sharing%20behind-the-scenes%2C%20connecting%20with%20people%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20orders%20came%20in.%20Now%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20queries%2C%20especially%20for%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20gone%20viral%20overnight%2C%20but%20it%20has%20grown%20steadily.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20keepsake%20that%20is%20full%20of%20soul%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Zainab%20Mukhtyar%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20about%20intimacy%20and%20permanence.%20%E2%80%9CTraditional%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20lovely%2C%20but%20they%20fade%20away%20within%20hours.%20With%20crochet%2C%20you%20can%20preserve%20that%20special%20moment.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20keepsake%20that%20couples%20can%20hold%20on%20to%2C%20just%20like%20their%20memories%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zainab's%20crochet%20brand%20focuses%20on%20the%20emotional%20value%20of%20each%20varmala.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496052%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EZainab%E2%80%99s%20crochet%20brand%20focuses%20on%20the%20emotional%20value%20of%20each%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzains_story%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZain%E2%80%99s%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Manya%2C%20Zainab%E2%80%99s%20idea%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20from%20a%20specific%20request.%20It%20was%20born%20out%20of%20her%20own%20reflections%20on%20weddings%20and%20memory.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20moment.%20It%20was%20just%20the%20thought%20that%20you%20could%20preserve%20your%20special%20day%20in%20a%20more%20meaningful%20way.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20began%20curating%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%2C%20she%20says%2C%20has%20been%20steadily%20growing.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20off%20immediately%2C%20but%20now%20I%20get%20new%20queries%20almost%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%20Each%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Etakes%20two%20to%20three%20days%20to%20make%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20flowers%20and%20the%20design.%20She%20uses%20acrylic%20yarn%20and%20adds%20beads%20to%20bind%20the%20flowers%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Zainab%2C%20the%20appeal%20lies%20in%20the%20emotional%20value.%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20goes%20to%20waste.%20The%20flowers%20don%E2%80%99t%20wilt.%20It%E2%80%99s%20handmade%20with%20love%20and%20care%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20couples%20can%20keep%20forever.%20I%20feel%20weddings%20are%20moving%20towards%20more%20sustainable%2C%20mindful%20choices%2C%20and%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Efit%20right%20into%20that.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20how%20sentimental%20they%20are%20and%20full%20of%20soul.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20crochet%2C%20why%20now%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Esays%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20Indian%20weddings%20are%20evolving.%20Once%20notorious%20for%20their%20extravagance%20and%20waste%2C%20younger%20couples%20are%20increasingly%20seeking%20ways%20to%20make%20their%20celebrations%20more%20personal%20and%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20always%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20fresh%20trends%20and%20styles%2C%20so%20when%20I%20came%20across%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20found%20them%20incredibly%20cute%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20could%20create%20a%20buzz%20at%20my%20wedding%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2026-year-old%20Shilpa%2C%20who%20tied%20the%20knot%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20ordered%20white%20%3Cem%3Emogra%3C%2Fem%3E-like%20flowers%20with%20an%20additional%20layer%20of%20crochet%20roses%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20piece%20cost%20me%20around%20Rs%204%2C300.%20The%20varmala%20is%20now%20framed%20in%20my%20living%20room%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20see%20when%20I%20wake%20up%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20couples%20mindful%20of%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20or%20eager%20for%20keepsakes%2C%20crochet%20varmalas%20offers%20a%20way%20out.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496056%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20couples%20mindful%20of%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20or%20eager%20for%20keepsakes%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoffers%20a%20way%20out.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzains_story%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZain%E2%80%99s%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFresh%20flowers%2C%20while%20undeniably%20beautiful%2C%20come%20with%20hidden%20costs%2C%20including%20environmental%2C%20financial%2C%20and%20emotional.%20Hours%20of%20refrigeration%2C%20long-distance%20transport%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20spent%20on%20garlands%20that%20last%20barely%20an%20evening.%20For%20couples%20mindful%20of%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20or%20eager%20for%20keepsakes%2C%20crochet%20offers%20a%20way%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20revivalist%20charm%20to%20it.%20Crochet%2C%20once%20dismissed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgrandmother%E2%80%99s%20hobby%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20now%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20slow%20fashion%20and%20handmade%20crafts.%20It%20carries%20a%20nostalgia%2C%20a%20tactile%20softness%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20intimacy%20that%20mass-produced%20items%20lack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20is%20the%20Instagram%20effect.%20A%20pastel%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eagainst%20a%20cream%20%3Cem%3Esherwani%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20a%20red%20%3Cem%3Elehenga%20%3C%2Fem%3Emakes%20for%20striking%20visuals%2C%20fuelling%20curiosity%20and%20desire%20among%20wedding%20planners%20and%20couples%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20craft%2C%20a%20community%2C%20a%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20not%20just%20designers%2C%20but%20entire%20communities%20of%20women%20artisans.%20At%20Enchanted%20Threads%2C%20Ananya%20ensures%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20proceeds%20go%20directly%20to%20her%20team%20of%20underprivileged%20women%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20For%20Manya%2C%20it%20has%20been%20about%20collaboration%20with%20fellow%20crochet%20artists%2C%20slowly%20expanding%20from%20a%20solo%20effort%20to%20a%20small%20creative%20team.%20For%20Zainab%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20pouring%20herself%20into%20every%20detail%2C%20bead%20by%20bead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecarries%20within%20it%20not%20just%20threads%20and%20knots%2C%20but%20also%20stories%20of%20empowerment%2C%20patience%2C%20and%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20are%20real.%20Tight%20timelines%2C%20lack%20of%20awareness%2C%20the%20lingering%20preference%20for%20fresh%20flowers%2C%20but%20so%20is%20the%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDFP7fzLSePO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDFP7fzLSePO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDFP7fzLSePO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Crochet%20by%20Enchanted%20Threads%20%7C%20India%20%7C%20Dehradun%20(%40enchanted_threads._)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20media%20coverage%2C%20rising%20interest%20among%20NRIs%2C%20and%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20sustainable%20wedding%20practices%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20no%20longer%20just%20a%20niche%20experiment.%20They%20are%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20mainstream%20wedding%20vocabulary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20not%20happening%20in%20isolation%3B%20it%20mirrors%20a%20larger%20shift%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F451310%2Fsustainable-wedding-love-story-avinash-tewari-namita-manohar-low-waste-wedding-recycled-decor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econscious%20weddings%20across%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Couples%20are%20increasingly%20swapping%20paper-heavy%20invitations%20for%20seed-paper%20cards%20that%20sprout%20into%20plants%2C%20replacing%20plastic-heavy%20d%C3%A9cor%20with%20biodegradable%20alternatives%2C%20and%20even%20turning%20to%20upcycled%20fabrics%20for%20their%20wedding%20outfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeen%20against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecome%20more%20than%20just%20a%20pretty%20keepsake%2C%20they%20are%20part%20of%20a%20powerful%20movement%20that%20redefines%20how%20we%20celebrate%20love%2C%20proving%20that%20tradition%20and%20sustainability%20can%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECouples%20can%20frame%20them%2C%20pass%20them%20down%2C%20or%20simply%20keep%20them%20folded%20away%2C%20soft%20with%20yarn%20and%20memory.%20In%20a%20wedding%20culture%20obsessed%20with%20grandeur%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eremind%20us%20of%20something%20simpler%20yet%20profound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELove%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20last.%20Why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20garlands%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757129400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496018%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20seen%20only%20in%20sweaters%20and%20cushion%20covers%2C%20crochet%20has%20now%20entered%20Indian%20weddings%20through%20crochet%20%E2%80%98varmalas%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20garlands%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20wilt%2C%20but%20last%20forever.%20Couples%20are%20embracing%20them%20as%20sustainable%2C%20sentimental%20keepsakes%20that%20turn%20a%20traditional%20ritual%20into%20timeless%20art.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496018%2Fcrochet-varmalas-indian-weddings-sustainable-ananya-malhotra-manya-jain-trending-garlands%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Floods%20Ravage%20Punjab%2C%203.5%20Lakh%20Struggle%20To%20Survive.%20Be%20Their%20Lifeline%2C%20Donate%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mohan%20Singh%20was%20preparing%20to%20harvest%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekharif%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecrops%20on%20his%20field%20this%20week.%20He%20was%20elated%3B%20it%20had%20been%20a%20great%20season.%20So%20picture%20his%20devastation%20when%20he%20walked%20out%20onto%20his%20field%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20and%20saw%20that%20the%20green%20had%20been%20replaced%20by%20steadily%20rising%20water.%20Mohan%20belongs%20to%20Gurdaspur%20in%20Punjab%2C%20which%20is%20inundated%20by%20the%20waters%20flooding%20the%20state.%20The%20relentless%20heavy%20rains%20are%20compounded%20by%20the%20dangerously%20high%20levels%20of%20the%20Sutlej%2C%20Beas%2C%20and%20Ravi%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20is%20drowning.%20It%20needs%20your%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDonate%20to%20help%20Punjab%20flood%20victims%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mohan%2C%20like%20the%203%2C54%2C000%20people%20(as%20of%205%20September)%20affected%2C%20did%20not%20have%20time%20to%20grieve.%20His%20only%20priority%20was%20ensuring%20that%20his%20family%20made%20it%20out%20of%20the%20house%20alive.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20escape%3B%20the%20only%20option%20was%20to%20wait%20and%20pray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496899%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20they%20saw%20a%20boat%20making%20its%20way%20to%20them.%20In%20it%20was%20Simranjit%20Singh%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Akal%20Relief%20Team%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391684%2Fcol-dr-rajinder-singh-started-akal-drug-de-addiction-centre-punjab-substance-abuse-alcoholism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPunjab-based%20NGO%20Kalgidhar%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20many%20conducting%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20on%20the%20ground%20supported%20by%20Donatekart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20possibility%20of%20salvaging%20the%20house%20or%20any%20of%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20belongings.%20But%20as%20they%20journeyed%20on%20the%20boat%20to%20the%20relief%20camp%20in%20Gurdaspur%2C%20Mohan%20broke%20down%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20fields%20are%20gone.%20I%20know%20I%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20sow%20anything%20for%20another%20year%20until%20the%20soil%20becomes%20fertile%20again%20and%20the%20mud%20is%20removed.%20What%20am%20I%20going%20to%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20are%20ongoing%20on%20ground%20to%20help%20the%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20Punjab%20floods%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496937%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERelief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20are%20underway%20to%20support%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20Punjab%20floods.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20had%20the%20answers.%20Harmeet%20Singh%2C%20who%20leads%20CSR%20(Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility)%20at%20Kalgidhar%20Trust%2C%20admits%20that%2C%20despite%20having%20conducted%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20for